column1: * AWS Pricing Calculator provides only an estimate of your AWS fees and doesn't include any taxes that might apply. Your actual fees depend on a variety of factors, including your actual usage of AWS services.

To take advantage of the increase in the allocated infrastructure resources budget, I improved upon the initial planned infrastructure by augmenting the availability of the application. With double the initial budget, I essentially doubled the resources in the initial plan - adding redundancy in the us-west-1 region for the following components: CloudFront Distribution, EC2 Instances, RDS, S3, VPC, Application Load Balancers, and Network Load Balancers.
